# Top-level workspace ignore rules

# Nested repository metadata
**/.git/

# ROS / catkin build artifacts
**/build/
**/devel/
**/install/
**/log/

# Python virtual environments and cache
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/env/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc

# Compiled artifacts
**/*.o
**/*.so
**/*.a

# VSCode or IDE local caches
**/.vscode/

# Exclude navigation subproject from top-level tracking
26-WrightEagle.AI-navigation/
